Everyone becomes concerned about the consequences if the Founder learns that Roger may return. Meanwhile, Stephen tries to destroy the machine the Founder has been using to train him; and Russell loses hope that the Refuge will ever be found and chooses to head out on his own with some other Tomorrow People.—Mikee
